platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: It took less than a minute for us to get hooked on this series all over again. The sequel to Rovios blockbuster puzzler polishes the feathery fun to a golden sheenand with more than just beautiful new graphics. Features like multi-stage levels, pig-punishing spells and choosing the order in which you fling birds make the game more irresistible than ever. Whether its your first Angry Birds game or your 10th, youll be flying high in no time.
